QuestData.Title: The Waking Shores Reverse Tour
QuestData.Description:
It's time to send you backwards. Not backwards in time, although we could do that, but have you fly the courses in reverse.
Get ready to see these courses in a different way.
Let's start with Serohs Gnikaw!
Wait. Waking Shores!
QuestData.LogDescription: Fly each of the reverse courses in Waking Shores.
